data.description: This home shows like new and is extremely well maintained. It is a 3br/2bath with garden tub and separate shower. Very large sparkling eat-in kitchen that has plenty of cabinet space and stylish appliances. Refrig., gar. disposal, stove/oven, dishwasher, washer/dryer, microwave, blinds convey. Backk yard is completely fenced with wood privacy fence. Two car garage. Conveniently located to Hwy 52, AFB and weapons station.There is a brand new HVAC installed in Sept. 2023. Roof installed Jan 2017 with complete architectural shingle replacement Jan 2017. Driveway extension Sept. 2023. Under Termite Bond.
